sequenceDiagram
  participant App as Caller app
  participant Redactor as Redactor SDK
  participant Provider as LLM provider
  participant Telemetry as Telemetry exporter

  App->>Redactor: wrap request metadata and optional content
  Redactor->>Provider: call provider through caller-owned client
  Provider-->>Redactor: response or stream event
  Redactor->>Redactor: redact content before telemetry export
  Redactor-->>Telemetry: safe GenAI metadata and redaction summary
  Redactor-->>App: provider response
